  56,61,‘ALA ‘EN NUBEDDILE ‘EMTHALEKUM WE NUNSHI’EKUM FI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  56,62,WE LEKAD ‘ALIMTUMU EN-NESH’ETEL-’ULA FELEWLA TEDHKKERUNE
